---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Embedded Finance - The Davinci Project" description="Integrate financial services directly into your platform.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Embedded Finance</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Integrate financial services directly into your platform with our secure escrow protocol.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What is Embedded Finance?</h2>
      <p>Embedded finance allows non-financial businesses to provide financial services directly within their platforms. With The Davinci Project's escrow protocol, you can offer secure digital asset transfers to your users without them ever leaving your ecosystem.</p>
      
      <h2>Key Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Secure multi-signature escrow for digital assets</li>
        <li>Seamless API integration with your existing platform</li>
        <li>Real-time transaction monitoring and status updates</li>
        <li>Compliance-ready infrastructure</li>
        <li>Multi-chain support</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Benefits</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Increase user trust and retention</li>
        <li>Create new revenue streams</li>
        <li>Reduce friction in peer-to-peer transactions</li>
        <li>Leverage blockchain security without blockchain complexity</li>
      </ul>
      
      <div class="cta-section">
        <h3>Ready to get started?</h3>
        <p>Contact our team to learn how embedded finance can transform your platform.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-primary) 0%, var(--bg-secondary) 100%);
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 600px;
  }
  
  .content-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }
  
  .content-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .content-section p, .content-section li {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .content-section ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .cta-section h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  
  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
  }
  
  .btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }
  
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent-green);
    color: #000;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .page-hero {
      padding: 7rem 0 3rem;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .container {
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
